{"url": "http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2016/06/14/mitch-mcconnell-muslims_n_10456658.html", "date": "2016-06-14", "content": "Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell (R-Ky.) criticized presumptive Republican presidential nominee Donald Trump\u2019s views of Muslim Americans, saying most Muslims living in the U.S. are \"patriotic.\"\n\"One of the points I think he's missing is, there are an awful lot of patriotic, loyal American Muslims,\" McConnell told HuffPost's Howard Fineman. \"In fact, they are the best sources we have to find these lone wolves in our country.\"\nTrump blamed Muslims in a speech Monday in the aftermath of the Orlando shooting, in which 49 people were killed and 53 others injured in a massacre at a gay nightclub. Trump said Muslims in the U.S. failed to\u00a0\u201cturn in the people who they know are bad,\u201d claiming they could have prevented both the attack in Orlando and the shooting in\u00a0San Bernardino, California.\nMcConnell opposes Trump's proposal to ban all Muslims from entering the United States, telling HuffPost he thinks it's a \"bad idea.\" McConnell said it's hard to \"target the bad guys,\" but suggested going after terror groups at their headquarters rather than putting a blanket ban on all Muslims entering the U.S.\nWatch a clip of McConnell above.\nEditor\u2019s note:\u00a0Donald Trump regularly\u00a0incites political violence\u00a0and is a\u00a0serial liar,\u00a0rampant xenophobe,\u00a0racist,\u00a0misogynist\u00a0and\u00a0birther\u00a0who has repeatedly pledged to ban all Muslims \u2014 1.6 billion members of an entire religion \u2014 from entering the U.S.", "title": "Mitch McConnell: There Are A Lot Of 'Patriotic, Loyal American Muslims'"}